## Mapping dom nodes to .svelte sources

### is very easy
```js
function findMetaEl(el) {
    while (el) {
        const file = el.__svelte_meta?.loc?.file;
        if (el !== toggle_el && file && !file.includes('node_modules/')) {
            return el;
        }
        el = el.parentNode;
    }
}
```

